===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|ablatif||the ablative case}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|ablātīvus||expressing removal}},<ref>{{R:American Heritage 1971|page=3}}</ref> from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|ablātus||taken away}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|auferō||I take away}}. The engineering/nautical sense is a {{back-form|ablate|nocap=1|lang=en}}

